rows.label: tlk70000020_03_msg0001
rows.name:
I saw the knighting
ceremony. Congratulations!

rows.label: tlk70000020_03_msg0002
rows.name:
People will continue to flock to
you and recognize your leadership.
You have that way about you.

rows.label: tlk70000020_03_msg0003
rows.name:
However, do not allow the
voices or convictions of
others to influence you.

rows.label: tlk70000020_03_msg0004
rows.name:
Stay true to yourself and your
beliefs. I will always be
here, looking out for you.
